Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.04,0:00:17.75,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.53,0:00:20.73,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要紧 茉莉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.00,0:00:21.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.75,0:00:24.45,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我找到了 线索
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.39,0:00:28.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定可以把茉莉带到蓝天下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.65,0:00:44.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这么慢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.24,0:00:53.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.16,0:02:36.75,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那么那个男人也许下次又会来袭击你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.05,0:02:41.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微让他尝了下苦头 应该暂时安全了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.10,0:02:44.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,大概会有一段时间他的手臂不能动了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.14,0:02:46.31,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.06,0:02:48.91,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.46,0:02:52.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道的吧 我不是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.81,0:02:55.10,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是叫夜祸人对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.41,0:02:56.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我都听说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.49,0:02:58.85,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.28,0:03:01.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我多少也有点心理准备的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.21,0:03:03.05,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,心理准备？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.99,0:03:07.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人不会那么简单就把一个少女留在家中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.04,0:03:10.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是有什么事情的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.33,0:03:12.05,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.42,0:03:15.67,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不讨厌你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.44,0:03:20.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.09,0:03:24.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.30,0:03:26.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.97,0:03:31.86,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人 依人 到上学的时间了 依人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.13,0:03:31.86,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,下午再去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.80,0:03:35.87,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,早上去拍朝霞了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.53,0:03:38.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,铁爪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.26,0:03:41.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.19,0:03:43.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,关系真好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.45,0:03:50.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然只有一点 但好像出现了类似坏死的症状
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.58,0:03:52.64,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,坏死？ 怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.35,0:03:55.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是把手垫在身体下睡觉的缘故吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.68,0:03:56.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.82,0:03:58.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这是不可能的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.63,0:04:00.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,从以前开始就是这样的体质
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.57,0:04:02.26,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,之前也有过类似的经历
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.47,0:04:03.74,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不去管它自己会好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.05,0:04:05.05,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.05,0:04:06.64,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,她是一个爱操心的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.03,0:04:09.07,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦您了 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.43,0:04:10.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,刚史 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.10,0:04:12.46,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,刚史 站住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.77,0:04:16.17,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,按照约定 给医生好好看过了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.41,0:04:17.73,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里有好好的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.90,0:04:19.41,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这点小事我不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.16,0:04:21.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那你告诉我发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.24,0:04:24.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你和夜祸之间发生了什么对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.53,0:04:26.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你想太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.18,0:04:29.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 刚史 站住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.37,0:04:33.87,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.03,0:04:36.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,实在很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.15,0:04:37.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,自己注意点 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.91,0:04:38.86,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,刚史
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.95,0:04:49.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 我来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.34,0:04:52.15,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才也联络过真名了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.31,0:04:54.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,叫姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.02,0:04:56.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.23,0:05:01.31,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我继续说了 她说找苍乃有事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.48,0:05:04.55,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,明天要是下雨的话就和依人一起来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.61,0:05:06.34,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.16,0:05:10.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,说详细的话等来了以后再说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.42,0:05:19.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,到了学校还这样不就和在家里时一样了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.17,0:05:21.80,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.17,0:05:23.45,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,现在正是好时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.88,0:05:25.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.63,0:05:28.41,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,正好是太阳从云里露出来的一瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.89,0:05:31.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,给茉莉看的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.35,0:05:35.46,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我想告诉她太阳是一种什么感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.94,0:05:37.09,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,被子也晒过了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.48,0:05:38.19,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,被子？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.48,0:05:40.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.61,0:05:43.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,约好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.40,0:05:47.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道啦 不会再出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.05,0:05:50.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,在依人带我去看天空之前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.62,0:05:58.83,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.54,0:06:03.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,明天真的要把她介绍给苍乃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.89,0:06:07.53,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 已经不能再隐瞒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.59,0:06:10.25,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么介绍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.22,0:06:15.94,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这个啊  说是朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.89,0:06:19.82,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你认为苍乃会同意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.38,0:06:22.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,她和我不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.20,0:06:23.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.19,0:06:26.51,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你站在相反的立场上想一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.82,0:06:29.83,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,苍乃某天带来一个陌生男人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.12,0:06:33.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,说是朋友 从今天开始住在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.97,0:06:34.87,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你能同意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.02,0:06:39.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你还真是什么都没有想过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.15,0:06:42.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那该怎么办好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.00,0:06:46.24,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有点牵强 但也只有一个方法了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.88,0:06:47.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,一个？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:50.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.51,0:06:53.45,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,恋人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.81,0:06:57.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我本来说是朋友就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.64,0:07:01.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,只是真名说这样比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.81,0:07:02.53,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.02,0:07:04.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊 没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.32,0:07:06.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.69,0:07:07.31,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.03,0:07:11.82,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.51,0:07:15.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉太阳像眼珠一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.33,0:07:19.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这个称为太阳打伞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.76,0:07:21.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,如果看见这个了 明天就会下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.86,0:07:23.02,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.30,0:07:25.34,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,天气预报也说要下雨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.85,0:07:28.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那先来练习一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.80,0:07:29.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,练习？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.84,0:07:30.39,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.22,0:07:34.17,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我是依人的恋人对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.69,0:07:44.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我去收被子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.34,0:08:08.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳公公的味道？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.21,0:08:13.05,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 晒过的被子有太阳的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.59,0:08:15.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳公公的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.44,0:08:16.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:21.47,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,像这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.27,0:08:25.31,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得好温暖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.40,0:08:28.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 这就是太阳的温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.69,0:08:30.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳公公的温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.78,0:08:31.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.38,0:08:33.87,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,咕…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.95,0:08:34.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.41,0:08:46.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我是依人的恋人对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.54,0:08:48.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.17,0:08:50.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 不要拿开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.88,0:08:57.02,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好温暖 好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.68,0:08:59.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.22,0:09:03.07,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人有喜欢的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.73,0:09:05.53,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,原来有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.95,0:09:07.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.86,0:09:08.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.06,0:09:11.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那 接吻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.03,0:09:17.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,别捉弄我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.66,0:09:19.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你看我像是在捉弄你嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.72,0:09:41.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.10,0:09:44.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人当真啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.23,0:09:46.07,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.44,0:09:49.26,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,才不会和依人亲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.63,0:09:50.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.59,0:09:54.99,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真期待明天啊 有很多话要对依人的姐姐倾诉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.19,0:09:56.24,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不用说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.53,0:10:00.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,除了「初次见面 我是四方茉莉 苍乃姐姐」之外的话都不要说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.74,0:10:02.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,苍乃？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.66,0:10:03.64,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,记住了没
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.62,0:10:07.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人的姐姐叫苍乃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.77,0:10:10.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪 我没提过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.61,0:10:16.05,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,森宫苍乃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.83,0:10:29.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,平常只要有一点声音就会醒的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.13,0:10:32.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 不过睡着了把她叫起来也不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.17,0:10:34.39,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,再等一会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.83,0:10:36.07,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.53,0:10:41.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那去买果汁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.16,0:10:42.95,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.25,0:10:48.39,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉 走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.00,0:11:08.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 没想到过了探望时间也还没醒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.74,0:11:11.74,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,也没办法嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.68,0:11:14.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定是在装睡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.17,0:11:18.86,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,可是那个感觉的确是在熟睡…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.28,0:11:21.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,苍乃小姐她…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:22.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.03,0:11:24.71,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,从什么时候开始住院的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.70,0:11:29.47,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,病倒的时候是搬来这之前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.06,0:11:31.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,大概3个月之前吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.81,0:11:32.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.71,0:11:35.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,在医院和依人认识就是那时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.75,0:11:36.73,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那之前呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.33,0:11:38.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,身体很好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.38,0:11:42.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然现在住院 但结果还是不知道什么病因
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.01,0:11:46.42,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,「可能只是过度疲劳」 医生这样说的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.72,0:11:47.41,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.11,0:12:00.87,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.74,0:12:05.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我走回去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.28,0:12:09.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我很久都没有一个人在街上走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.54,0:12:11.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 那别太晚了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.29,0:12:12.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.30,0:12:44.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.28,0:12:47.05,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,漏水越来越厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.37,0:12:52.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.92,0:12:57.47,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,暂时还是不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.68,0:13:06.34,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.44,0:13:19.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道是我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.07,0:13:23.09,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我从小依那里听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.53,0:13:24.37,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,说是叫茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.24,0:13:25.95,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.07,0:13:29.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,最近总算恢复力量了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.95,0:13:31.51,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,使用过度的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.61,0:13:36.42,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你倒下是因为这个原因？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.98,0:13:40.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不老不死的夜祸人会倒下也只有这个理由
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.55,0:13:44.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,而且那段时间你出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.14,0:13:47.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不过算了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.79,0:13:51.26,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,反正总有一天会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.81,0:13:54.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,在永生的时间里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.78,0:14:03.82,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.49,0:14:05.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.47,0:14:08.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,说谎 这不可能 因为依人是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.59,0:14:09.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.13,0:14:12.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我唯一的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.22,0:14:32.05,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.22,0:14:35.10,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,说清楚点 放还是不放
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.31,0:14:36.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你真狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.31,0:14:39.59,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是你的妹妹 当然和你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.59,0:14:40.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,和那个没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.35,0:14:43.91,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我从没听过吃火锅要放白菜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.91,0:14:48.29,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,要是没有那浸透了锅底味道的白菜还算什么火锅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.73,0:14:52.66,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 这里就一半一半来弄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.87,0:14:53.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.28,0:14:55.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.60,0:14:57.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,来得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.16,0:15:00.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你吃火锅会放白菜吧 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.08,0:15:02.69,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不放的 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.80,0:15:06.42,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,可能不会放吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.63,0:15:08.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧 这下出决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.01,0:15:10.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 还没
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.40,0:15:10.86,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,放的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.58,0:15:16.17,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姐… 姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.27,0:15:23.53,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那你是问了护士小姐后 来追我们的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.46,0:15:28.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不过没赶上依人你们坐的车
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.24,0:15:30.85,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不用那么勉强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.28,0:15:32.31,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,对身体不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.01,0:15:35.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 我正好想吃肉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.40,0:15:39.73,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,可是不回医院没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.01,0:15:43.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我有外出许可 所以暂时待在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.67,0:15:44.46,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.56,0:15:47.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,而且这也是茉莉小姐寄住这里的条件
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.69,0:15:50.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人输了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.97,0:15:54.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了啦 明天会去和医生好好谈的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.90,0:15:56.93,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这下就不能做H的事情了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.21,0:15:59.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那是当然的 再说我根本没做过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.25,0:16:01.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.30,0:16:02.94,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我差点被依人…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.61,0:16:06.09,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不要胡说八道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.44,0:16:07.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么时候做了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.95,0:16:10.34,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,做了哦 昨天在被子上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.32,0:16:13.58,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是你引诱我的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.58,0:16:14.41,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,引诱！？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.61,0:16:16.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.06,0:16:17.33,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.56,0:16:19.33,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,实在很不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.64,0:16:22.93,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我想我对依人的印象也改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.17,0:16:24.47,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,都说不是了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.70,0:16:29.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那个被子晒过以后有太阳的味道嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.53,0:16:30.47,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.47,0:16:32.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,就是哪个啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.77,0:16:34.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,要我送你们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.28,0:16:37.51,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不必劳驾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.01,0:16:39.02,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,走 小依
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.60,0:16:40.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,再见 变态依人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.96,0:16:41.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我说那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.86,0:16:48.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.67,0:16:54.70,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我有一个请求
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.30,0:17:12.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真没用啊 来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.59,0:17:15.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.56,0:17:23.46,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉心咚咚跳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.46,0:17:26.47,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真的一定非今天不可吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.94,0:17:29.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,仅仅是进去的话 还是在下雨天的周日比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.44,0:17:32.85,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,现在想进去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.44,0:17:35.86,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,如果被谁发现了 马上逃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.28,0:17:37.74,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.23,0:17:50.70,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,只有这里窗关的比较松
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.45,0:17:56.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,比想象中的要宽敞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.55,0:17:57.73,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因为什么人都没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.75,0:18:02.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,平常很吵的 所以觉得比较窄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.60,0:18:07.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.48,0:18:08.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.28,0:18:13.55,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那里是我的座位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.06,0:18:15.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是真名的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.94,0:18:21.37,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这样的感觉呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.75,0:18:25.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,只有在电视上看过学校
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.00,0:18:29.39,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,并不是什么很有趣的地方 还很无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.79,0:18:33.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,老师也很烦 上课也很容易犯困
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.67,0:18:35.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 原来你都知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.55,0:18:39.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,体育课也很累 早上也要起早
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.09,0:18:43.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,可你不是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.17,0:18:47.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这一点就已经很幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.64,0:18:50.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.23,0:18:53.80,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是从这里拍天空的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.15,0:18:57.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 拍摄地方在…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.34,0:19:03.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.58,0:19:04.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.91,0:19:08.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,躺在这里拿着照相机朝向天空
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.24,0:19:14.09,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真的 好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.42,0:19:15.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.56,0:19:18.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是学校里最能令人平静的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.59,0:19:22.83,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那我在睡觉时 依人就躺在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.10,0:19:23.80,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.01,0:19:26.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,在我睡觉时
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.83,0:19:29.74,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,在我不知道的世界里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.20,0:19:31.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就会变成你知道的世界的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.19,0:19:36.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我会带你出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.49,0:19:55.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真安静呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.23,0:19:59.67,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 因为已经很晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.39,0:20:04.58,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你听说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.05,0:20:06.91,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,人为什么会睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.68,0:20:12.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,人在睡觉的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.81,0:20:16.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,痛苦不安憎恨都会全部丢弃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.36,0:20:22.70,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,然后用这一颗轻松的心去迎接早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.78,0:20:25.91,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,痛苦消失在黑暗里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.44,0:20:30.70,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,明亮的天空和新的时间迎接人们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.23,0:20:55.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,夜祸是由人丢弃在夜里的痛苦不安集成的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.48,0:21:01.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,人最忌讳讨厌的另外一个自己
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.11,0:21:04.42,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么让我活过来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.45,0:21:08.79,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想活在没有依人的世界里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.79,0:21:16.19,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,所以夜祸总是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.58,0:21:17.31,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.63,0:21:19.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不得不一个人活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.96,0:21:20.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.18,0:21:22.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.61,0:21:39.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过的对吧 没有在捉弄你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.78,0:21:48.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.28,0:23:33.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,繭子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.47,0:23:34.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.39,0:23:35.73,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,关于饭团的…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.01,0:23:38.29,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,非要你吃的话你会选择哪一种
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.48,0:23:40.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,柴鱼味的和克克味的…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.48,0:23:40.35,Default2,NTP,0,533,0,,OKaKa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.48,0:23:40.35,Default2,NTP,267,0,0,,KaKaO
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.37,0:23:41.61,Default1,NTP,0,533,450,,{\fs112.5}差
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.94,0:23:41.61,Default1,NTP,533,0,450,,{\fs112.5}劲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.04,0:02:37.01,FBT,NTP,0,0,360,,{\fad(500,500)}祭 血
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.93,0:23:45.94,FBT,NTP,420,0,224,,灰色的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.44,0:01:15.85,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}羽根が白く光り 眩しく飛んで行く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.22,0:01:22.47,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}心だけ乗せて欲しいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.81,0:01:30.23,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}冷たい手を伸ばす 届かない…知ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.57,0:01:37.68,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}だけどいま触れたい君に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.95,0:01:44.08,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}懐かしい風には あの頃の舟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.36,0:01:52.67,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}幻が思い出を見せた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.30,0:02:02.16,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}「忘れない」誰かの声が切なく響く
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.56,0:02:07.60,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}始まる予感にふるえて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.77,0:02:15.94,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}「忘れたい」願う自分がわからない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.14,0:02:27.35,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,2000)}待っている 揺られながら夢ひとつを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.44,0:01:15.85,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}雪白闪亮的羽毛飞向远方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.22,0:01:22.47,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}它要是能带上我的心意多好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.81,0:01:30.23,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}伸出冰冷的双手 明明知道触摸不到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.57,0:01:37.68,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}可是现在想碰触到你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.95,0:01:44.08,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}令人怀念的微风像那时候的小船
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.36,0:01:52.67,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}呈现出梦幻的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.30,0:02:02.16,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}「不要忘记」耳边想起悲伤的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.56,0:02:07.60,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}害怕那要发生什么的预感
